faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己又係啲思想本來就比較負面嘅人，好容易崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔開心又唔想同人講費事畀人話成日喺度放負<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊堅持落去直到相見嘅一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e5f3633ab570e35108aa6932c340e0721bfb6a","tid":1742430,"uid":40792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b448ea99624c2be970db1f8f0bb1d88f19e33352","tid":1742430,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:49:52.000Z","msg":"你好勇敢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:54:04.000Z","msg":"我唔勇敢啦，成5個月，我而家先走上前。<br />\n比起所有死左受傷同被捕既手足，我微塵黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a51926f02b469982f25b816d2dd3c50345f537","tid":1742430,"uid":40792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69a4f98ddbf2dc37e251d84b3f22a054f9a2f794","tid":1742430,"uid":165625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:51:36.000Z","msg":"手足加油 你從來都唔係自己一個 你仲有我哋大家！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然已經冷靜左，但都仲係好想喊"},{"pid":"409dcff0b868e4e06d32525fa3640bc2c3145ff6","tid":1742430,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:54:52.000Z","msg":"帶埋手足既信念繼續活下去<br />\n最近聽過好多感動嘅說話，呢一句都算係最大聲"},{"pid":"b8422206c6f5b0d9e65daf62422966eb70d8dc5a","tid":1742430,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aec61c7878e6a3f73292e938bb51608a1ada36d","tid":1742430,"uid":40792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:47:04.000Z","msg":"我既生活同將來係為左死去同受傷既手足而繼續活下去。<br />\n<br />\n今晚自殺念頭極